A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: One of the most boring Star Wars movies since the prequels. Many of scenes were loaded with exposition and had none of the interesting aspects that made The Force Awakens great. Many of the plot elements in this movie were redundant and created more questions about the Star Wars universe than answers. On the other hand\, the movie has gorgeous cinematography and some good ideas. The execution and the god awful\, misplaced humor brings this film down drastically.
